docs.lead_paragraph: ARRIVAL. OF THE U. S. STORE-SHIP SUPPLY. The Supply, Lieutenant-Commanding ANDREW F. V. GRAY, arrived, yesterday forenoon, from Rio de Janeiro, from which port she sailed on the 11th ultShe had a fine run up to the Equator-which she crossed on the 24th ult.-and as far north as 20??, since which time she has experienced light winds and calms.

headline.main: NEW-YORK CITY.; Mayor's Office. Will of the Lare Anson G. Phelps. FIGHT BETWEEN NOTED PUGILISTS. Board of Governors. Burial of Alderman Murray.

docs.lead_paragraph: HEALTH COMMISSIONERS.--At a meeting of the Health Commissioners on Wednesday, the following statement was received from the Health Officer: To His Honor the Mayor and Commissioners of Health, City of New-York: SIRS: At a meeting of your Honorable Board some few days ago, I was requested to state to-day the Susanna of the ships Susanna and Grotto, still lying to the lower Bay.

headline.main: EUROPE.; THE LATEST FROM LONDON. ARRIVAL OF THE KANGAROO.

docs.lead_paragraph: The mail steamship Kangaroo, J. F. JEFFREY, Esq., Commander, sailed from Liverpool on the 7th, arrived at this port yesterday morning . Her advices have been anticipated by the North Star, but the following dispatch furnishes a few hours later from London:

docs.lead_paragraph: THE SOUTH-STREET BURGLARY.-EDMOND GRIFFITH, who was arrested for attempting to rob Mr. CAREY'S house, on South-street, Tuesday morning, and shooting private-watchman BUCKLEY, was yesterday formally commotted to the Kings County Jail by Justice CORNWELL, on the affidavit of BUCKLEY, who charges him with an attempt to Bill.
